        "title":  "Courage the Cowardly Dog  [v1.4.4]",
        "description":  "[h1]The Bagge Family Farmhouse[/h1]\r\nThe Bagge family farmhouse from [i]Courage the Cowardly Dog[/i].\r\n\r\n[hr][/hr]\r\n\r\n[h2]Roadmap[/h2]\r\n A lot has been done so far — mostly optimizing and fixing the models — and now that most of the issues have been addressed and (hopefully) fixed, I can start focusing on what really matters: populating the map with more props and finish the outside\r\n\r\n[h2]About the outside[/h2]\r\nThe outside will be accessible once the inside is in a good place. I\u0027m slowly adding things out there to make it feel less empty — but right now there\u0027s almost nothing outside yet.\r\n\r\n[hr][/hr]\r\n\r\n[h2]Watch it being made[/h2]\r\nI sometimes stream myself developing the map on Twitch:\r\n[url=https://twitch.tv/nordbo_]twitch.tv/nordbo_[/url] [b](@nordbo_)[/b]\r\n\r\n[h2]❤️ Thank you[/h2]\r\nHuge thanks to the streamers over on Twitch who\u0027ve given feedback and support on the map — and to everyone in the comments leaving feedback. I really appreciate it!\r\n\r\n[hr][/hr]\r\n\r\n[h2]Credits[/h2]\r\nFarmhouse model by its creator on Sketchfab:\r\n[url=https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/courage-the-cowardly-dog-bagge-farmhouse-584f0d2e5d32457198b7dc9a3894b88a]Courage the Cowardly Dog — Bagge Farmhouse[/url]",
